Sat Aug 31 15:08:08 UTC 2024 - Dirk Müller <dmueller@suse.com>

- update to 1.20.0:
  * Fix the admin_register fixer to avoid rewriting when there
    are duplicate ModelAdmin classes in the file. Issue #471.

