- update to 1.18.0:
  * Support Django 5.1 as a target version.
  * Add Django 5.1+ fixer to rewrite the check keyword argument
    of CheckConstraint to condition.
  * Add fixer selection options: --only <name>, --skip <name>,
    and --list-fixers.

